OL,6,FFE BROMIGE - MODERNIST ARCHITECT       
OL,8, What does a demolished amusement arcade
OL,9, in Jaywick, A Grade two building in    
OL,10, Harrow and W.H. Smith have in common?  
OL,12, I speak to Professor Bruce Peter of the
OL,13, Glasgow School of Art to find out about
OL,14, the man who designed the most awesome  
OL,15, building of my childhood.              
