OL,6,FMARK PARKER - DIRECTOR,BEARDED LADIES  
OL,7, In this episode I catch up with my     
OL,8, childhood friend Mark Parker. Mark     
OL,9, played the machines in the Sunspot and 
OL,10, when leaving school, embarked on an    
OL,11, interesting career in the video games  
OL,12, industry forCEidos & I.O. interactive. 
OL,14, He is now Producer, Writer and Partner 
OL,15, atCThe Bearded LadiesGwho are          
OL,16, responsible for the highly rated Mutant
OL,17, Year Zero and The much anticipated     
OL,18, Myasma Chronicles. Mark talks to me    
OL,19, about the older systems, playtesting   
OL,20, and of course the Sunspot Arcade! 2/21 
