OL,5,EBYTE HIGH NO LIMIT _04        V (.,    
OL,6,FTELETEXT PEOPLE - IAN MORTON-SMITH     
OL,8, In the early 1970s Mort was the first  
OL,9, BBC news Sub Editor to work on the new 
OL,10, service called CEEFAX. He moved to the 
OL,11, USA to start Chicago's Keyfax and then 
OL,12, later returned to Blighty to run C4's  
OL,13, upstart service 4TEL                   
OL,15, I was privileged to speak with Mort and
OL,16, Julie to record their experiences      
OL,17, working at all these teletext services.
