OL,8, Russia 1991, the Soviet Union is       
OL,9, collapsing, A chance meeting with      
OL,10, engineers at a Moscow TV tower results 
OL,11, in Steve becoming in charge Russia's   
OL,12, first teletext services.               
OL,14, Steve explains his love for the medium 
OL,15, and shares his recollections of running
OL,16, a teletext system during volatile times
OL,17, of the Eastern Bloc.                   
