OL,8, Ian shares with us stories of how he   
OL,9, became the last editor of Ceefax before
OL,10, its merger with the BBC web based      
OL,11, service.                               
OL,13, Sport was one of the most popular      
OL,14, services on Ceefax and there are a few 
OL,15, tales of sackings of Football managers 
OL,16, and match winners that would not of    
OL,17, occurred had it not been for Ceefax.   
