OL,8, Ian Irving was one the medium's first  
OL,9, ever recognised artist and is cited as 
OL,10, a contemporary of many pixel artists   
OL,11, who used the format.                   
OL,12, Ian tells us his story of working at   
OL,13, Ceefax then moving to Intelfax and     
OL,14, 4-Tel.                                 
OL,16, Ian also worked on a ground breaking   
OL,17, project for deaf children 'Hands Up!'  
OL,18, on Channel four was a completely unique
OL,19, programme that can be viewed on YouTube
