OL,5,EBYTE HIGH NO LIMIT _18        V (.,    
OL,6,FA HISTORY OF DIY COMPUTERS             
OL,7, Before the Home computers became       
OL,8, ubiquitous and a technology we can not 
OL,9, live without, they were hobbies and    
OL,10, self built projects assembled by the   
OL,11, luminaries home computing.             
OL,12, This episode looks at the origins of   
OL,13, kit computers, in the US and UK, the TV
OL,14, Typewriter, the MK14, System 1, and 101
OL,15, In Yugoslavia with it's embargo busting
OL,16, Galaksija.                             
OL,17, The show includes recollections of the 
OL,18, users of these machines and a very     
OL,19, special interview with the Creator of  
OL,20, Galaksija, Voja Antonic.         18/21 
