OL,6,FPHONE PHREAKING W/PATRICK & CODY       
OL,7, In this episode we enjoy the           
OL,8, recollections of Patrick, @cgnfridays  
OL,9, and Cody, @pranfunkels as they discuss 
OL,10, hacks and tricks to get free calls on  
OL,11, phone systems like their hero, Matt    
OL,12, Broderick and try not to get caught... 
OL,13, with varying consequences.             
OL,15, They explain what innocent, inquisitive
OL,16, kids can get up to with telephones and 
OL,17, how they took over voice mail systems  
OL,18, to create a BBS without the knowledge  
OL,19, that the US Hacker community were      
OL,20, already at it too!               21/21 
